'''Von Shul''' was a member of the [[Intendant caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. A [[Consul/Legends|Consul]] of [[Domain Shul]], he developed a rivalry with Consul [[Melaan Nar|Melaan]] of [[Domain Nar]]. [[Supreme Overlord]] [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra]] ordered them to put aside their differences, and concentrate on defeating the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]].

